sourcesContent:
let searchInputStyle = {
  width: "calc(65.9vw - 28px)",
  height: "30px",
  outlineWidth: "0px",
  boxSizing: "border-box",
  fontSize: "17px",
}

let listContainerStyle = {
  display: "inline-block",
  minWidth: "100%",
  marginTop: "10px",
  height: "84vh", 
  overflowY: "scroll",
  zIndex: -1,
}

let searchProfileButton = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  marginRight: "2px",
  textAlign: "center",
  cursor: "pointer",
  userSelect: "none",
  fontWeight: "bold",

  normal: {
    width: "98px",
    height: "27px",
    paddingTop: "3px",
    color: "black"
  },

  focused: {
    width: "94px",
    height: "25px",
    border: "2px solid #07405b",
    paddingTop: "1px",
    color: "white"
  }
}

export {
  searchInputStyle,
  listContainerStyle,
  searchProfileButton,
}
